Source tapes/config.tape

Set Theme "Catppuccin Latte"

Hide
Type "export CTP_FLAVOR=latte"
Enter
Type "cd ~/Projects/catppuccin-zsh"
Enter
Type "source catppuccin.zsh-theme"
Enter
Sleep 2s
Show

Type "git status"
Enter
Sleep 1s

Type "ls -la"
Enter
Sleep 1s

Screenshot assets/latte.png
Sleep 500ms
